<br>
&quot;I love a good expedition.&quot; Apollo perked a brow and flashed his amazing smile.<br>
<br>
&quot;But we will not do this hap-hazardly. We will assemble a expedition team, and gather supplies and do this the right way.&quot; Apollo nodded as he walked around Hypnos and pulled out a seat for his guest.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do sit, sit down.&quot; Apollo smiled. Apollo pushed a large gilded chair infront of a table and sat down near Hypnos.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do tell me more about your idea's.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=zephyr>Zephyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(11/18/01 4:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=193.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Comming of Winter</span><hr size=1>          There is a breeze that comes from the west and Zephyr blinks in right by Apollo.<br>
