<br>
&quot;First and for most I would like to ask one question. Who are you? Secondly, what are you doing in my temple? And thirdy, What do you want?&quot;<br>
<br>
Apollo's bluntness was well known throughout Olympus, and this was no exception. Apollo crossed his arms over his chest tightly and awaited this...thing to answer his questions. Apollo shook the golden locks from his eyes and perked a brow.<br>
